In the INTEREST OF D.H., Minor Child, R.D., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1552 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals from an order terminating her parental rights in her child pursuant to Iowa Code chapter 232 (2018). AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
